{"tid":2132764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英外相藍韜文表示侯選人被DQ破壞了聯合聲明所保障港人的權利和自由","createTime":"2020-07-30T14:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T16:59:39.000Z","uid":53844,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2edd0e648f25a197a98116ae3015535dde63f2c6","tid":2132764,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:35:58.000Z","msg":"I condemn the decision to disqualify opposition candidates from standing in Hong Kong&rsquo;s Legislative Council elections.<br />\n<br />\nIt is clear they have been disqualified because of their political views, undermining the integrity of &lsquo;One Country, Two Systems&rsquo; and the rights and freedoms guaranteed in the Joint Declaration and Hong Kong&rsquo;s Basic Law.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong authorities must uphold their commitments to the people of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n我譴責取消反對派候選人參加香港立法會選舉的決定。<br />\n<br />\n顯然，他們由於所持有的政治觀點而被取消資格，這破壞了一國兩制的完整性以及《中英聯合聲明》和《香港基本法》所保障的權利和自由。<br />\n<br />\n香港當局必須恪守對香港人民的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/foreign-secretarys-statement-on-hong-kong-election-disqualifications\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fforeign-secretarys-statement-on-hong-kong-election-disqualifications&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=235b9167\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/foreign-secretarys-statement-on-hong-kong-election-disqualifications</a>"},{"pid":"99366fc0a5e66e9617659fc4b33b489c8f0748fe","tid":2132764,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbbd9c0c91b5874b2293c38226f7d432058f358","tid":2132764,"uid":67454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-